    "Fig 17, presents some real-time results for object detection models.",
    "This research has introduced an innovative early detection system for forest fires employing a UAV equipped with an NVIDIA Jetson Nano onboard and a camera.",
    "The study assessed the efficacy of YOLOv5 and YOLOv8 models for object detection, comparing them with the CNN-RCNN model for classification.",
    "Additionally, a ground station application was developed to collect data from the UAV.",
    "The findings revealed comparable accuracy between YOLOv5 and YOLOv8 for object detection, achieving an accuracy of approximately 89%."
